<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241477>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 31. Belciana and Diphteroides spp., adults (25 – 30) and male genitalia (31). 25. B. pinratanai sp. n., female, paratype, Thailand, slide GB 8300 (GB); 26. B. pinratanai, sp. n., male, paratype, Thailand, slide MJP 707 (MJP); 27. B. scorpio, female, Thailand; 28. B. scorpio, male, North Vietnam, slide GB 7411 (GB); 29. B. scorpio, female, North Vietnam, slide GB 7365 (GB); 30. D. kendricki, male, Irian Jaya, slide GB 7354 (GB); 31. Ditto, male genitalia, slide GB 7354 (GB)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241477/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241481>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41 – 45. Belciana and Diphteroides spp., male (41) and female (42 – 45) genitalia. 41. B. scorpio, Thailand, slide GB / ZSM N 4215 (ZSM); 42. D. kendricki, Irian Jaya, slide GB 7372 (GB); 43. B. biformis, Sumatra, slide GB / ZSM N 4158 (ZSM); 44. B. hemodoides, Borneo, slide GB 7389 (GB); 45. B. sp., Irian Jaya, slide GB 7363 (GB). Most distinctive characters are marked by lines." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241481/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

